# {{lb|en|grammar}} A [[noun]] that is [[morphologically]] related to a [[verb]] and similar to it in meaning; in [[English]], this might be a [[gerund]] (ending in ''-ing''), [[infinitive]], or other noun derived from a verb.
#: ''Brisk '''walking''' is good exercise.''
#: ''We scored a ''' win'''.''

